ke":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5399a833eb65d913fe0d099d24f4a53b16a4228f","tid":750401,"uid":176318,"like":258,"dislike":9,"score":249,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T00:42:41.000Z","msg":"一向都知，但如果想更多人唔買<br />\n<br />\n可以直接去書展佢地攤位，公然大聲叫市民唔好買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"琴日我先講完<br />\n<br />\n今日即刻有人好似我講咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/示威者快閃現身書展-籲罷買-三中商/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%BF%AB%E9%96%83%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%E6%9B%B8%E5%B1%95-%E7%B1%B2%E7%BD%B7%E8%B2%B7-%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86%2F&d=%2Bo3dCIM5i4F2u9Sbvt8AmwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=96cc2318\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%BF%AB%E9%96%83%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%E6%9B%B8%E5%B1%95-%E7%B1%B2%E7%BD%B7%E8%B2%B7-%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86%2F&h=f23197fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/示威者快閃現身書展-籲罷買-三中商/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/37619975_10155556860232374_8041628458423418880_n_ksdQy_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F37619975_10155556860232374_8041628458423418880_n_ksdQy_1200x0.jpg&h=57677aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦透過內地公司，全資持有香港三聯書店、中華書局和商務印書館（三中商）股權，事件近月再度引起關注。有示威者今日在書展穿上「罷買三中商，咪益中聯辦」的上衣，以快閃方式走到三中商展區前站立示威，呼籲民眾罷買。<br />\n<br />\n由圖片可見，八名示威者身穿白色上色，各人背後各有字詞，合併後可以組成「罷買三中商，咪益中聯辦」的口號，又高舉著「三中商係奸商」等標語。他們走入書展並於三中商展區前站立。<br />\n<br />\n《壹週刊》2015年時亦曾引述大陸工商局文件報道，指中聯辦透過一間大陸神秘空殼公司，迂迴持有及經營聯合出版集團，並實益擁有《文匯報》、《大公報》、《香港商報》，甚至成立網絡媒體「橙新聞」。<br />\n<br />\n今年5月《鏗鏘集》再次報道事件，指查冊發現「聯合出版集團」股東，是今年初獲委任為中聯辦秘書長的文宏武，大股東「新文化事業（香港）發展」則由廣州「廣東新聞化事業」持有，該公司唯一股東是中聯辦。「聯合出版集團」首任董事長李祖澤回應港台查詢時承認，集團屬國有資產，但否認經營書店有政治任務。"},{"pid":"55c5fdbf08658c465c364020d68349220cbdbbc4","tid":750401,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:07:55.000Z","msg":"去開序言買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb6214f866feafc7ec19a1ef364337120a59c48","tid":750401,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0327dd8a7d86bab9ea1be87bc2bc663abdfaee51","tid":750401,"uid":47674,"like":53,"dislike":7,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"c104fdbb7ecaf66ccb7b856f28ffb463020e6452","tid":750401,"uid":83685,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T00:47:09.000Z","msg":"想問吓大眾o唔ok，諗住去書局買書"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T01:09:50.000Z","msg":"新加坡兩頭蛇<br />\n出埋晒啲殘體中文書<br />\n可免則免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:35:52.000Z","msg":"我的𡚒鬥 45萬字冇刪減中文版 得簡體冇繁體<br />\n但中國係禁書  南洋出版社出簡體唔知有乜用"},{"pid":"b18b4af586625e0381a5b280dd6a3adff3b830b8","tid":750401,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"681a91f247bf7315288b42c8db2fa4f2abccb50a","tid":750401,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"但點解去商務 中華 三聯<br />\n都係見到日本講政治D書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"大把中國禁書 三間都冇賣<br />\n賺錢掛"},{"pid":"f5e0779b7a78fe67d441bbc49facd34b4872b908","tid":750401,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddb6214f866feafc7ec19a1ef364337120a59c48","tid":750401,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0327dd8a7d86bab9ea1be87bc2bc663abdfaee51","tid":750401,"uid":47674,"like":53,"dislike":7,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"c104fdbb7ecaf66ccb7b856f28ffb463020e6452","tid":750401,"uid":83685,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T00:47:09.000Z","msg":"想問吓大眾o唔ok，諗住去書局買書"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-